EXCEPTION — Embeddable Widgets
===============================

Notwithstanding the NonCommercial restriction above, the interactive widgets
published at jjlmoya.es/utilidades/ (calculators, tools, and similar embeddable
components) may be freely used, embedded, or redistributed in any context,
including commercial websites and applications, provided that:

  1. The original watermark or attribution notice ("jjlmoya.es") visible within
     the widget is preserved and not removed, hidden, or obscured in any way.
  2. The watermark must remain clearly legible to end users.

Removing or hiding the watermark voids this exception and the standard
CC BY-NC 4.0 terms apply in full.
